Fri Jun  7 19:53:44 2002  Petr Baudis <pasky@ji.cz>:

	* intl/brazilian_portuguese.lng, intl/bulgarian.lng,
	intl/catalan.lng, intl/czech.lng, intl/danish.lng, intl/dutch.lng,
